content"><a href="/research/research-for-the-world/politics/us-and-middle-east"><h2>What really went wrong in the Middle East</h2><p>America’s concern over Communist Russia and its attempt to establish a Pax Americana led it to make disastrous foreign policy decisions in the Middle East, the consequences of which can still be felt today, argues Fawaz Gerges in a new book.</p></a></div></div></div></div></div></div><div data-index="2" class="slick-slide" tabindex="-1" aria-hidden="true" style="outline:none;width:33.333333333333336%"><div><div aria-hidden="true" tabindex="-1" style="width:100%;display:inline-block"><div class="home-hero-slide"><div class="home-hero-slide__content-wrapper"><div class="home-hero-slide__content"><a href="/research/research-for-the-world/society/working-mothers-employment"><h2>The identity struggle facing working mothers</h2><p>Working mothers can struggle to find a balance between their identities as mothers and their identities as professional women. New research by Lucia Garcia-Lorenzo explores these tensions and outlines how we can provide better support.  </p></a></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class="home-slider__footer"><a class="buttonstyled__ButtonStyled-sc-kr8cig-0 kpFGEI primary home-hero-slide__link" href="/research/research-for-the-world/sustainability/climate-legislation-and-litigation" aria-hidden="false">Read More<span class="i button__icon "><svg width="24" height="24" role="img" focusable="false" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="black" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"><path d="M7.99997 7L12.293 11.293L7.99997 15.586L9.41397 17L15.121 11.293L9.41397 5.586L7.99997 7Z"></path></svg></span></a><a class="buttonstyled__ButtonStyled-sc-kr8cig-0 kpFGEI primary home-hero-slide__link" href="/research/research-for-the-world/politics/us-and-middle-east" aria-hidden="true">Read More<span class="i button__icon "><svg width="24" height="24" role="img" focusable="false" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="black" xmlns="http: